metadata.name: The diner at the end of the road #1
metadata.description:
We are all familiar with these places that are close to where we live and that are somehow part of our lives. But can a place that doesn't exist be familiar? Something that simply universally represents these places so different from each other and so recognizable to everyone?  
This project tries to recreate these places and sensations.

Created by Simone Pompei with the help of an AI.
